(WHAS11) -- The UK Wildcats are in the spotlight as they gear up to face the Auburn Tigers. At 7 p.m. Thursday, UK will face off against the Auburn Tigers on ESPN. 
Auburn was in the top 10 at the beginning of the season but are now out of the top 25 teams in the country. Kentucky though is coming off of a bye week and they have their eyes set on a fifth victory. 
Kickoff time is at 7 p.m. on ESPN with the game being played in Lexington, Kentucky. Read or Share this story: http://on.whas11.com/1Lvmul7 TOP VIDEOS
